{"tid":1226000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急呼籲】人多一恐慌就好易人踩人，應如何自保？","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T12:27:27.000Z","uid":70786,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"667cdfdbff047e709b80fc05a0a6fdc35b2ebd88","tid":1226000,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:18:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好重要請花少少時間睇一睇</span></span><br />\n睇完林鄭個記者會相信大家都慶過火屎<br />\n我好驚616同617會係破天荒咁多人<br />\n而佢又再一次確認警方於612當日處理手法絕對正確<br />\n無疑係助長警隊歪風同黑警氣焰<br />\n唔知佢地嚟緊會用咩部署同裝備<br />\n可能會用到更高級武力<br />\n一旦引起恐慌，有機會重現當年蘭桂芳人踩人慘劇<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161225/photo/bkn-20161225060003663-1225_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161225120618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161225%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161225060003663-1225_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161225120618&h=eeb4b989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位有必要學識點樣保護自己性命安全<br />\n１發生突發事件時，保持冷靜，觀察四周環境。<br />\n２一旦場面失控，儘快逃離現場，切勿用手機拍攝及回頭觀望，以免阻礙人群逃生。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要最重要最重要！！！</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">３萬一不幸被推跌，立即瞓側並捲曲身體，用手保護頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人踩人死者大多數都唔係被踩死，而係<strong>窒息致死</strong><br />\n如果你平瞓或趴地，被踩時肺部就擴張唔到！！！所以要瞓側，瞓側，瞓側！！！<br />\n<br />\n學識點樣保護自己，話埋俾你地身邊嘅人知！"},{"pid":"83b501e113b86a9ae5463fb488db818bb59f8e6e","tid":1226000,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"解放軍都殺到嚟呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n即時龍和道 大量解放軍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1225694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1225694</a>"},{"pid":"6f20fffd024c7ebbb01f298e84c198a07337c805","tid":1226000,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"大家一定要知呀！！！"},{"pid":"1266c1d90304565a96f7cba7c29cda0fa6f2a49e","tid":1226000,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"睇完留個emoji推上去呀！<br />\n聽日可能有解放軍混入群眾／警方當中生事<br />\n甚至可能重用「死Ｘ人可保Ｘ年穩定」策略 ！！！"},{"pid":"cf9cab94ddfdd980f5b517aa0b8a110d67e69cc2","tid":1226000,"uid":24223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"161ccabb52c156a0b8b30bdccde35157153594ad","tid":1226000,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d13b2deb917f8eace546cb8daf83a177d0e32b8e","tid":1226000,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3caf8e725cd6b418a02d1a5d17947b787f6fe9","tid":1226000,"uid":47866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"嗰日添馬公園撤退嘅時候<br />\n如果唔係班巴打醒目識得拆咗AIA個圍欄<br />\n唔係嘅話，嗰日好大機會會發生人踩人"},{"pid":"19a60c01839266a6abceab01e3d5bb8e4ad8dc88","tid":1226000,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3caf8e725cd6b418a02d1a5d17947b787f6fe9","tid":1226000,"uid":47866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:40:11.000Z","msg":"嗰日添馬公園撤退嘅時候<br />\n如果唔係班巴打醒目識得拆咗AIA個圍欄<br />\n唔係嘅話，嗰日好大機會會發生人踩人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"香港人冇咩危機感<br />\n溫室得太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fce39203927f82c0247a5568c660e1950e8dacb","tid":1226000,"uid":165958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046da7256c9b2ffb1eaa915f230d0cce81c942a0","tid":1226000,"uid":207217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837128507c3c4d5c4ccd823de8c20b4356f0552e","tid":1226000,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06